[I] A declarative statistical visualization library for Python

[T] Vega-Altair is a declarative statistical visualization library for Python.
[T] With Vega-Altair, you can spend more time understanding your data and its
[T] meaning. Vega-Altair's API is simple, friendly and consistent and built on
[T] top of the powerful Vega-Lite JSON specification. This elegant simplicity
[T] produces beautiful and effective visualizations with a minimal amount of
[T] code.

[U] https://github.com/vega/altair

